c: 3
v: 198
t: "Kinnih immay sinni Rabbik meesiteh yan mari jannootay weeqaytitte guba kak gexxa lon teetil waarak, tamah Yallih xaquk tan Qibnaytiinô konnabay Yallih xaquk geeni kinni, Yallih xaqul tanim kay Amri oggolak Suge marah koros Addunyal edde hatakak Sugte dago duyyê Baxak khayrih Aysuk Raqta"